flowchart TD
    subgraph "Presentation Layer"
        API[API Layer<br/>Controllers<br/>Middleware<br/>Auth]
        Console[Console Layer<br/>Menu<br/>Factory Pattern]
    end
    
    subgraph "Application Layer"
        Services[Application Services<br/>IQuantityService<br/>DTOs<br/>Business Logic]
    end
    
    subgraph "Infrastructure Layer"
        Infra[Infrastructure<br/>Repositories<br/>DbContext<br/>Auth Service<br/>Redis Cache]
    end
    
    subgraph "Domain Layer"
        Domain[Domain<br/>Quantity Classes<br/>Unit Definitions<br/>IQuantity Interface]
    end
    
    subgraph "Data Layer"
        DB[(SQL Server<br/>Database)]
        Cache[(Redis<br/>Cache)]
    end
    
    subgraph "External"
        Client[Client<br/>HTTP Requests]
        User[User<br/>Console Input]
    end
    
    %% API Flow
    Client -->|HTTP POST<br/>QuantityRequestDto| API
    API -->|JWT Auth<br/>Rate Limiting| API
    API -->|IQuantityService.Convert/Add/etc.<br/>QuantityRequestDto| Services
    Services -->|Create Quantity objects<br/>from DTO| Domain
    Domain -->|Business Logic<br/>Convert/Add/Subtract| Domain
    Domain -->|Result Quantity| Services
    Services -->|HistoryRecord| Infra
    Infra -->|Save to DB<br/>Cache Invalidation| DB
    Infra -->|Cache History<br/>30min TTL| Cache
    Services -->|QuantityResultDto| API
    API -->|HTTP 200<br/>JSON Response| Client
    
    %% Console Flow
    User -->|Menu Selection<br/>Input Values| Console
    Console -->|Create Quantity<br/>Direct Instantiation| Domain
    Domain -->|Operations<br/>Convert/Add/etc.| Domain
    Domain -->|Results| Console
    Console -->|Display to User| User
    
    %% Dependencies (project references)
    API -.->|Depends on| Services
    API -.->|Depends on| Infra
    Services -.->|Depends on| Domain
    Services -.->|Depends on| Infra
    Infra -.->|Depends on| Domain
    Console -.->|Depends on| Domain
    
    %% Infrastructure connections
    Infra -->|EF Core| DB
    Infra -->|StackExchange.Redis| Cache